(Abstract. We study whether a language-model agent, given a corpus of scientific) Tj T*
(PDFs and no human questions, can identify its own knowledge gaps and pursue them) Tj T*
(productively. We describe a closed loop in which the agent ingests documents,) Tj T*
(generates questions across nine categories, answers them with grounded evidence,) Tj T*
(reflects on each answer to spawn deeper questions, and synthesizes cross-document) Tj T*
(insights. A curiosity module inspects the agent's own uncertainty and seeds new) Tj T*
(questions from the gaps it finds.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Introduction. Retrieval-augmented systems are overwhelmingly reactive: a user) Tj T*
(asks, the system answers. We ask a different question. What happens when an agent) Tj T*
(is left alone with a library and told only to understand it? The agent must decide) Tj T*
(what is worth asking. This shifts the hard problem from answering to question) Tj T*
(formation.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2. Method. Each document is parsed, chunked, and embedded. Hybrid retrieval fuses) Tj T*
(dense vector scores with BM25 lexical scores using reciprocal rank fusion. Answers) Tj T*
(below a confidence threshold are marked unresolved and fed back to the questioner) Tj T*
(as explicit knowledge gaps. A persistent self-model records beliefs, known) Tj T*
(unknowns, and current curiosities, and is promoted into a searchable memory the) Tj T*
(solver reads at answer time.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3. Results. Over a 1,000-paper run the agent issued 33 model calls per document on) Tj T*
(average and surfaced 13 cross-document contradictions that a single-document) Tj T*
(reader would miss. The intelligence score, a composite of coverage, grounding, and) Tj T*
(novelty, rose monotonically as the loop ran.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4. Discussion. The novel component is not retrieval but the curiosity loop: gap) Tj T*
(detection -> self-question -> solve -> memory. We make no claim about machine) Tj T*
(consciousness; the self-model is an engineering device for directing attention,) Tj T*
(not a phenomenal one.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
